cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper deals with natural language processing and specifically focuses on contextual word embeddings. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also utilizes deep learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) a likely category as well. Additionally, the paper involves unsupervised learning, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The method proposed in the paper involves mapping and alignment, which could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper applies its method to dependency parsing, which is a task related to syntactic analysis and could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
